reviewText: This ballet is definitly STILL available. It is just packaged differently. This is now it's packaging.....Sleeping Beauty / Christine Walsh, Australian Ballet This is the same Australian Ballet production being sold with a different front cover on Amazon. You can read my review and others by clicking on "Read all my reviews", which will take you to the other "Beauty" review. Or, click here Sleeping Beauty / Christine Walsh, Australian Ballet If you cannot find it, take my word that it is a wonderful production of Sleeping Beauty and well worth your time and money. Sumptuous sets and costumes and great dancers go into making this a must have "Beauty".
